         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395"><!-- p3l5-r11 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Hd1e108">Rubrica 11</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De vaniloquio et multiloquio</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
      ¶ De vaniloquio et multilo
      <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>quio Rubrica. 11
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>SAlomon in prouerbiis.
      <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>c. 15. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e127">Respon
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>sio molis frangit iram: sermo du
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>rus suscitat furorem. Lingua pla
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>cabilis lignum vite.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e137"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e139"> 16. c. Qui sapiens cor.
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>de est appellabitur prudens: et qui dulcis elo
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>quio maiora percipiet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e148"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e150"> 17. c. Cum obse
        <lb ed="#V" n="42" break="no"/>crationibus loquitur pauper: et diues effabi
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>tur rigide. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e162">¶ Socrates in exhortationlbus. c. 2. Esto
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>quidem modo suauis: verbo vero facetus. <!--193.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>Est autem suauitas quidem salutare occurrem
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>tes. facetie vero alloqui eos lepidibus verbis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e180">¶ Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 5. Pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>sequatur te verbum pacis et iustitie. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e186"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e188"> c. 6.
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>Uerbum dulce multiplicat amicos: et miti
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>gat inimicos. Lingua gratiosa in bono ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>mine abundat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e202">¶ Quidius de arte amandi. lib. 2. Asperitas
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>odium seuaque bella mouet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e208">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e212">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola ad romanos.
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>c. 12. Benedicite: et nolite maledicere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e223">¶ Cato. Capitulo. i. Saluta libenter. Blan
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>dus esto. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e229">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e233">¶ Uersificator fabularum esopi. 38 fina.
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>Dulcia pro dulci pro turpi turpia reddi
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>Uerba solent: odium lingua fidemque parit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e245">¶ Bernardus in scilicet de probatione viciorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>c. 3. Gratus vir: lingua cuique placere solet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e251">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e255">¶ henricus samariensis li. 2. Stillet in ore
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>fauus: sed mente resultet oliua.
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>Et non sit totus sensus in ore tuus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>Factaque si desint: non desint verba benigna.
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>Nam multos caros mellea lingua parit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e267">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e271">¶ Gaufridus in poetria. c. 108. Mors et vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>ta coherent Inimanibus lingue. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e277">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e281">¶ Ricardus iudex venusinus vel de pertracta
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>tione nuptiarum. c. i. Pacem sermo bonus
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>gignit: et gaudia mestis
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>Cordibus infundit: tristitiamque leuat.
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Ignis aqua: verbisque bonis extiguitur ira.
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>Sermo bonus quandoque magis quam fcausa porant.
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Nil sermone bono gratius esse solet. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
